{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[Leap Through the Night with Your Shadow \u2013 Thrilling Shadow Clone Action]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world of night, control the power of shadows as the protagonist dashes around with exhilarating moves, taking down enemies alongside their shadow clones in this fast-paced shadow clone action game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961830/extras/Battle.gif?t=1730856724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[High-Speed \u00d7 Thrilling Action]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run along walls, dash through the air, and race across stages with various moves to smash through your enemies with bold, dynamic action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961830/extras/Move.gif?t=1730856724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[Shadow Skills]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress through stages, unlock shadow skills that allow you to battle alongside your shadow clone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>[Roguelike Elements]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After clearing each floor, gain random skills to customize your character to your liking. Enjoy exciting action that\u2019s uniquely tailored to you.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730856724","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961830/page.bg.jpg?t=1730856724","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961830/00f3ddbf2b90f1f39e339d9a68499cebc76b07ed/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730856724","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961830/00f3ddbf2b90f1f39e339d9a68499cebc76b07ed/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730856724","categories":[{"description"